                  <zone forceUpdate='true' h='14891' id='31' type-v2='text' w='18525' x='36896' y='9568'>
                    <formatted-text>
                      <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#59a14f' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='18'>💼</run>
                      <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#59a14f' fontname='Tableau Bold'>Best Job Segment</run>
                      <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#59a14f' fontname='Tableau Bold'>Student</run>
                      <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#59a14f' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='16'>74.7%</run>
                    </formatted-text>
                    <zone-style>
                      <format attr='border-color' value='#898989' />
                      <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                      <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
                      <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                      <format attr='padding' value='8' />
                    </zone-style>
                  </zone>
                  <zone forceUpdate='true' h='14891' id='32' type-v2='text' w='19233' x='55421' y='9568'>
                    <formatted-text>
                      <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontsize='18'>📞</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#4e79a7'>Best Contact Channel</run>
                      <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#4e79a7'>Cellular</run>
                      <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontsize='16'>54.3%</run>
                    </formatted-text>
                    <zone-style>
                      <format attr='border-color' value='#898989' />
                      <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                      <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
                      <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                      <format attr='padding' value='8' />
                    </zone-style>
                  </zone>
                  <zone forceUpdate='true' h='55257' id='33' type-v2='text' w='24658' x='74654' y='9568'>
                    <formatted-text>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run bold='true'>Recommended Campaign Strategies</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#f28e2b'>1. Target high-response segments</run>
                      <run>
Prioritise students aged 18–24 and retired clients aged 65+, while also considering balance, loans, and previous outcome.

</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#b6992d'>2. Use better contact channels</run>
                      <run>
Prioritise cellular contact and reduce reliance on unknown contact methods.

</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#59a14f'>3. Time campaigns carefully</run>
                      <run>
Run pilots in March, September, October, and December, but validate small-sample months before scaling.

</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#499894'>4. Avoid over-contacting</run>
                      <run>
Stop or change strategy after repeated unsuccessful contacts, because six or more contacts show lower conversion.

</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#4e79a7'>5. Use duration insight for training</run>
                      <run>
Longer calls are associated with success, so train agents to improve engagement, but do not use duration as a pre-call targeting variable.

</run>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#9d7660'>Ethics note</run>
                      <run>
Age and job can guide customer-needs messaging, but the campaign should avoid discriminatory exclusion. Customers should have clear opt-out options, and contact frequency should be controlled to avoid harassment.</run>
                    </formatted-text>
                    <zone-style>
                      <format attr='border-color' value='#b4b4b4' />
                      <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
                      <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
                      <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    </zone-style>
                  </zone>
                  <zone h='40366' id='34' name='1.4 Previous Outcome Effect' w='39414' x='688' y='24459'>
                    <zone-style>
                      <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                      <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                      <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                      <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    </zone-style>
                  </zone>
                </zone>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
